versions.source:
version: 2.1
orbs:
  foo:
    commands:
      foo:
        steps:
          - checkout
commands:
  myfoo: foo/foo
  bar:
    parameters:
      hello:
        type: string
        default: world
    steps:
      - echo <<parameters.hello>>

executors:
  default:
    parameters:
      tag:
        type: string
        default: "curl-browsers"
    docker:
      - image: circleci/buildpack-deps:<< parameters.tag >>

jobs:
  hello-build:
    executor: default
    steps:
      - echo:
          message: "Hello, build!"
